data.description: Wow, what a great opportunity to purchase this all brick RANCH home that's very convenient to Interstate travel. Tucked away on a large .91 Acre lot, this cozy home has a ton of potential with just a little updating. Features include three bedrooms, one tile bath, large family room and living room, kitchen and dining room combination. There is a huge detached garage that already has power and very easily can have water hooked up. The back yard is huge and already has space for your garden! If you're a flower lover, you're going to be shocked at all the beauty that will pop up in your yard next Spring!
